  "description": "Use this skill when writing SOQL aggregate queries in Apex \u2014 GROUP BY, GROUP BY ROLLUP/CUBE, HAVING, COUNT/SUM/AVG/MIN/MAX, AggregateResult, and date grouping functions. Trigger keywords: soql aggregate groupby apex, count sum group by salesforce, aggregateresult get alias, having clause soql, rollup cube subtotals. NOT for relationship subqueries or inner queries (use apex-soql-relationship-queries), NOT for the Reporting API or Analytics Wave API.",
